<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-kappa-lost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3595398); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3595398&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720562" alt="Jack Kappa Lost" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3595398)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-kappa-lost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3595398); return false;">Jack Kappa Lost</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>本文系<a href="/comte-de-monte-cristo">基金会伯爵</a>续篇，为保证最大阅读体验，还请阅读前篇。</p>
<hr />
<p>评论区有花絮看（小声）</p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
